						               													<description>In Penguin Smash, players are a group of penguins that can not take the cold. To stay warm in the south pole, they figure out that they can just smash each other to keep body temperature high! (What a genius penguin!)&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Penguin Smash is a dexterity game in which players will put one hand on the table and take turns flipping one card from his/her own deck of penguin cards by the other hand. If the total number of the revealed penguin cards matches the corresponding penguin player's status card, everyone must race to SMASH that player's hand on the table. The first player to smash the penguin player's hand scores all the corresponding penguin cards. The player who manages to SMASH the most penguin will be the master of penguin smash and win the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Be alert! Some special cards will put your penguin into sleep or sent it to dinner, and therefore making the SMASH not easy as you may imagine.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
